msgstr "For some reason, the var/cache/ directory could not be cleaned up. Please clean it up by manually connecting to the server and delete all files and symbolic links under the chamilo/var/cache/ directory, except the .htaccess file. On Linux: # find var/cache/ \( -type f -or -type l \) -not -name .htaccess -exec echo rm -v \{} \;"

